仔, 但冇果種「漂白」或者「光潔如新」既感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(有一兩個銀仔直頭可以反射到自己個輪廓, 不過影落唔係太明顯)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LpAzw7D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLpAzw7D.jpg&h=c05fa085&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/digSiNF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdigSiNF.jpg&h=206f66bb&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好似呢種咁, 就洗極都只係「乾淨咗」<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xXqjJeW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxXqjJeW.jpg&h=121a57cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TFBnF1D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTFBnF1D.jpg&h=afb24518&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gke4UmG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fgke4UmG.jpg&h=ac9f3741&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而仲有個最大問題 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我有個銀仔本身係白色既<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Dk6CuVi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDk6CuVi.jpg&h=8ea38875&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n而另外個銀仔本身係金色, 洗完變咗好淺色, 淺到分唔到佢係金定白 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1qesR8Z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1qesR8Z.jpg&h=3fda4040&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nbtw 試咗幾款銀仔, 效果最顯著係十蚊餅, 不過冇影"},{"pid":"0dff62787a0a654f0dc252e4b256a39ea8b4a972","tid":2170954,"uid":69221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T13:02:49.000Z","msg":"最簡單咪牙膏"},{"pid":"d4ec57138c7499bdc15c5b585f84a0720366a285","tid":2170954,"uid":66817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"45c7c9f0086b92b0feb0fe66b21cd60e6a5f379d","tid":2170954,"uid":76382,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"